            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Stacks of self-supporting metallic foils of aluminum",
                "and copper of purity greater than 99.99% and of",
                "thickness 14-mg/cm**2 and 23-mg/cm**2, respectively",
                "were used. Copper foils were interspersed with aluminum",
                "foils of varying thicknesses acting as energy",
                "degraders, while the aluminum stack was prepared",
                "without any degrader foils."
